## Description {#details}

Holds the information from a dbg&#95;value node through SDISel.

We do not use <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/sdvalue">SDValue</a> here to avoid including its header.

Definition at line 133 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/codegen/lib/codegen/selectiondag/sdnodedbgvalue-h">SDNodeDbgValue.h</a>.

### setIsInvalidated() {#a456b1fecfa3d25a0b2a4822332cdd044}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype="void llvm::SDDbgValue::setIsInvalidated ()"
  labels = {["inline"]}>
setIsInvalidated / isInvalidated - Setter / getter of the &quot;Invalidated&quot; property.

A <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/sddbgvalue">SDDbgValue</a> is invalid if the <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/sdnode">SDNode</a> that produces the value is deleted.
